<BaseLayout title="About — Gacha Codex" description="Unofficial fan database for Neverness to Everness — tier list, builds, boss guides and gacha mechanics.">
  <h1>About Gacha Codex</h1>
  <div class="prose-game max-w-prose">
    <p>
      Gacha Codex is an unofficial fan database for <strong>Neverness to Everness</strong>,
      a 2026 urban-supernatural gacha RPG by Hotta Studio (published by Perfect World).
      We are not affiliated with the developer or publisher.
    </p>

    <h2>What you'll find here</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>A weekly-updated <a href="/tier-list">tier list</a> covering every released character.</li>
      <li><a href="/characters">Character build guides</a> — recommended weapons, teams and rotations.</li>
      <li><a href="/boss">Boss strategies</a> for Abyss and overworld encounters.</li>
      <li><a href="/guides/reroll">Reroll</a> walkthroughs and <a href="/banners/current">current banner</a> coverage.</li>
      <li>A growing <a href="/faq">FAQ</a> on gacha mechanics, pity systems and game economy.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What we're <em>not</em></h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Not the official wiki — for the canonical word, visit Hotta Studio's channels.</li>
      <li>Not a replacement for community guides on Reddit or Discord — we link to those whenever they're the best source.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Found an error? See the <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
